OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777385514
OL,3,CPetrol station owner losing thousands
OL,4,Cevery month to fuel thefts
OL,6,FThe owner of a Southampton petrol
OL,7,Fstation says the recent rise in fuel
OL,8,Fprices is costing him thousands, due
OL,9,Fto drivers leaving the forecourt
OL,10,Fwithout paying.
OL,12,FBen Lawrence has run Lawrence's
OL,13,FGarages in Sholing, and other areas of
OL,14,Fthe county for many years.
OL,16,FHe says he's seen a 45% rise in people
OL,17,Fstealing fuel - since the war in Iran
OL,18,Fbegan.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
