FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777385514
OL,3,CPetrol station owner losing thousands
OL,4,Cevery month to fuel thefts
OL,6,F"We are determined to keep costs down
OL,7,Ffor motorists. That's why we have
OL,8,Fextended the 5p fuel duty cut twice
OL,9,Funtil September and will continue to
OL,10,Fmonitor the situation."
